entry.title: getumbrel/umbrel
entry.summary: A beautiful personal/home server OS for self-hosting with an app store. Buy a pre-built Umbrel Home with umbrelOS, or install on a Raspberry Pi 4, any Ubuntu/Debian system, or a VPS.

entry.title: 274056675/springboot-openai-chatgpt
entry.summary: 超级AI大脑一个基于Spring Boot架构，支持web，Android，IOS，H5多端应用，使用了OpenAI的ChatGPT模型实现了智能聊天机器人。用户可以在界面上与聊天机器人进行对话，聊天机器人会根据用户的输入自动生成回复。同时也支持画图，用户输入文本，便可以自动制作文生文生图。未来会接入：文心一言、通义千问、MOSS等国产AI大模型，持续更新中，更多功能等着你来解锁

entry.title: liberu-ui/genealogy
entry.summary: Nuxt 2 and Vue 2 client for genealogy project. Family tree and genealogy data processing website software client.
